	   <tr><td colspan=2>ZsaZsa - your prob is you have a wep in your primary hand slot. you must take that out so you can put your instrument in your secondary hand. unfortunately even when you get dual weild, you cannot have a wep AND a instrument&nbsp;&nbsp;=(  just one or the other<br><br>Taamas Starsinger<br>35th Season<br>House of Wargoth<br>Saryrn<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
