<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=98821815680824></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f98821815680824><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=4&mid=98821815680824>RE: New bard and drumming</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=4&mid=98821815680824#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=41254><span id= >Rashia</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>1 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Apr 25th 1:02 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am Rashia, 35th seasoned bard on The Rathe server.&nbsp;&nbsp;You should really start druming now!  The best way to do this is to create a section in your hotbox with inventory slots.  Place in slot 1: your primary weapon slot, slot 2: your secondary weapon/off hand slot, slot 3: an inventory slot with a weapon, insturment or a bag that holds the instruments and weapons, etc.  Then keep this hotbox open at all times.  When you need to swap out your weapon for you instrument just use it instead of opening your inventory screen.  Always keep in mind to remove your primary weapon first, then pick up your instrument and place it in your secondary/off hand slot.  You will not be able to equip a weapon with an instrument at any level UNLESS you get an instrument that will allow you to do so.  These instruments are only received at very high levels. I believe one might even come from a plane, but not absolutely sure.  I just know that I have found them on this website when looking for bigger and better item to quest/hunt for.  In addition, these instruments have really sweet effects.  I cannot wait to obtain one for myself.<br>Stay safe in your travels and have a blast with your bard. :)<br>&nbsp;<br>Mistress Rashia</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
